beer.beer_description:
A full-bodied, very hoppy brew with citrus, pine, fruity notes, and a nice dry, bitter finish!
This West Coast-style IPA is true to its style as it is very hop-forward with just enough malt character and alcohol to balance it out.

Hop: low-moderate citrus (orange and grapefruit), floral, pine resin
Malt and Yeast: Minimal contribution
